episodes.title: Epstein files: What the documents show about Kansas City connections
episodes.description:
3.5 million pages.   That’s the number of Jeffrey Epstein files the Department of Justice recently released after lawmakers passed the Epstein Files Transparency Act last year.  Kansas City, Missouri, is referenced in the files more than 540 times.
